while ensuring cost efficiency, quality standards, and timely delivery. Drives material cost
reduction strategies, negotiates prices, and oversees contract administration. Proactively
addresses risks, resolves non-conformance issues, and aligns with market trends to
support operational and strategic goals.
2. Tasks and Responsibilities
Describe the tasks and responsibilities in more detail. Use bullet points.
• Identifying, evaluating and selecting vendors to meet internal business needs;
• Continuously monitoring/seeking and implementation of material cost reduction via
different methods and strategies, lead price negotiation;
• Ensuring adhere to requirements (delivery time, quality standards, etc.);
